04:27.267 --> 04:29.060
at the pits, in Minsk.

04:30.603 --> 04:32.730
Or the vans at Chelmno,

04:33.231 --> 04:36.025
but these were the deeds
and demands of others.

04:36.567 --> 04:38.278
I issued no such orders.

04:39.153 --> 04:42.115
Our work was paperwork,

04:43.324 --> 04:45.034
our war a numerical one.

04:46.411 --> 04:50.248
