09:22.812 --> 09:24.897
Do you ever think about going back?

09:25.898 --> 09:27.149
[Klaus] To Germany?

09:27.650 --> 09:29.777
Um, I don't know.

09:30.695 --> 09:31.904
I'm told things.

09:33.656 --> 09:34.740
What things?

09:36.117 --> 09:39.662
Oh, the Jews, clawing power back,

09:40.246 --> 09:43.082
taking jobs,
corrupting everything, like before.

09:44.584 --> 09:48.045
But, of course, there are plenty
of them here too so...

09:49.171 --> 09:54.468
