20:06.455 --> 20:09.541
[Rafi] Aharoni's out there now running
reconnaissance in Buenos Aires

20:09.625 --> 20:11.084
with our guy at the Embassy.

20:11.168 --> 20:13.462
Our contact's daughter, Sylvia Hermann,

20:13.545 --> 20:16.465
has agreed to take us to
Klaus Eichmann's family home.

20:16.757 --> 20:20.510
